  "answer": "311 request volumes in flood-prone Austin ZIP codes show mixed trends compared to last year. ZIP code 78741 saw a 12.1% decrease (from 12,092 to 10,627 requests), and 78702 dropped by 4.3% (from 19,294 to 18,463). Meanwhile, 78704 experienced a 3.7% increase (from 19,924 to 20,659), and 78721 had a slight 1.6% decline (from 8,214 to 8,082).",
